  <brief_title>Maintaining the Head Extension by an Assistant Decreases Dental Contact</brief_title>
  <official_title>Maintaining the Head Extension by an Assistant Decreases Dental Contact Between Laryngoscope Blade and Maxillary Incisors During Direct Laryngoscopy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
